Jean d'Yd https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_d%27Yd 0 Jean d'Yd was the stage name of Jean Paul Félix Didier Perret. He was a French actor and comedian, and was born in Paris on the 17 May 1880. He died in Vernon, Eure, France on the 14 May 1964. Jean_d'Yd was the_stage_name of Jean_Paul_Félix_Didier_Perret . He was a_French_actor_and_comedian , and was_born in Paris on the_17_May_1880 .
